OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fclear skies for most tonight. Cloudier
OL,7,Facross the far southwest, with the
OL,8,Frisk of some showers developing here.
OL,9,FLocal frost and fog in the northeast.
OL,10,FStaying windy in the south where it
OL,11,Fwill remain pretty mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAnother warm and sunny day
OL,14,Ffor most. Cloudier skies towards
OL,15,Fsouthwestern areas and also Northern
OL,16,FIreland later, with the risk of a few
OL,17,Fshowers developing. Staying breezy in
OL,18,Fthe south.
